{"tid":131593,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"從前有班賊","createTime":"2017-02-23T07:15:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-26T05:11:27.000Z","uid":19275,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"561e0ae5eb73fbd115233239f724b52e472abb21","tid":131593,"uid":19275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T07:15:15.000Z","msg":"強姦非禮老屈毆打乜都做齊<br />\n重要無人拉到佢地<br />\n3萬幾個賊一路生活無憂<br />\n<br />\n點知有幾個伙記犯法犯到上埋電視<br />\n不過好在放左兩年有薪假先拉左<br />\n重要放兩年就坐翻兩年<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後成班賊就條氣唔順<br />\n曬馬曬左萬幾人<br />\n屌你老母！不嬲犯法都唔拉嫁啦點解依家先拉？！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我由始至終都係講緊賊，絕對唔係講警察，因為警察唔會咁，賊先會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"360239dfc412b3cb365809bf4149fdfeb5f74a48","tid":131593,"uid":19275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T07:41:37.000Z","msg":"有個賊負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6713f9a803f860bf4fbecab6d5ecc97bdcffcc1","tid":131593,"uid":34771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T02:08:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/215438/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/215438/page/1</a><br />\n樓主好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6997b8916d59b2b0546ac6d91336c3222f1dc4d","tid":131593,"uid":35296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T05:11:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/215438/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/215438/page/1</a><br />\n樓主好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}